{"tid":637005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大盜掘寶　證江口沉銀傳說屬實","createTime":"2018-04-21T12:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T15:02:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ead0047d6f3a9c0d67029bfbb6f6e3db1af4bc01","tid":637005,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180421/20368467?_ga=2.74575506.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368467%3F_ga%3D2.74575506.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=2dab682b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368467%3F_ga%3D2.74575506.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=268e7110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180421/20368467?_ga=2.74575506.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大盜掘寶　證江口沉銀傳說屬實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/a1002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2Fa1002a.gif&h=1d908a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■當局開放江口沉銀遺址予民眾參觀。　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國歷來不缺「寶藏」傳說，劉伯溫寶藏、石達開寶藏、李自成寶藏&hellip;&hellip;但以張獻忠寶藏最負盛名。2010年江口沉銀遺址被定為四川眉山市級文物保護單位，官方相信張獻忠沉銀於此，但史學界對「江口沉銀」一說，一直存有爭議。直到2016年，警方偵破一宗盜掘文物案，證實傳說不但屬實，且惹來盜賊垂涎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「尋寶訣」流傳數百年<br />\n<br />\n數百年來，眉山彭山區江口鎮流傳這樣一首童謠「石龍對石虎，金銀萬萬五，誰人識得破，買到成都府」。據說張獻忠兵敗後，把「大西國」的金銀財寶秘藏起來，為了將來能找到寶藏，便叫人設計了這個「尋寶訣」。但事實是清兵入關後，張將部份金銀財寶裝船運走，不料在彭山境內遭攔住，雙方展開大戰，幾船金銀財寶也在戰爭中沉入江底，不知所終。<br />\n<br />\n直到2016年10月，重慶警方破獲一宗特大盜掘古文化遺址案，發現文物大盜帶同專業設備，夜間潛入江口沉銀遺址河道區域盜挖，隨後將其賣給文物販子獲取暴利，並估計其已經作案長達4年，終證實江口沉銀一說。同年12月26日，當局在江口沉銀遺址進行首次考古發掘。<br />\n<br />\n每日頭條/《重慶晨報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n明代蜀藩王金寶首出土　張獻忠寶藏值37億<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n張獻忠「屠蜀」殺10萬人　吃人肉<br />\n<br />\n張獻忠「屠蜀」殺10萬人　吃人肉<br />\n<br />\n明代蜀藩王金寶首出土張獻忠寶藏值37億"},{"pid":"6da5888cc23cd03de484494fce80f7aff6472503","tid":637005,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d04f9263b9ba6f0bb7df20e07fc8d73003a77f47","tid":637005,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公安醒目 等人掘晒先拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c550bced81749fea756013eb84a0e8fa09f2e55a","tid":637005,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"天生萬物以養人 ，人無一物以報天<br />\n殺殺殺殺殺殺殺！"},{"pid":"d42bb1d78ca28f30d0bedb0131adfd98c412544a","tid":637005,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04f9263b9ba6f0bb7df20e07fc8d73003a77f47","tid":637005,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公安醒目 等人掘晒先拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"賊王。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58671b54b92f0c874e4ac7eff86f4dd4c78212a","tid":637005,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04f9263b9ba6f0bb7df20e07fc8d73003a77f47","tid":637005,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公安醒目 等人掘晒先拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"賊王。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif